# Release Quality Gates

- Run `./scripts/lint.sh` and `./scripts/test.sh` before opening a PR.
- For frontend-impacting changes, also run `npm --prefix frontend run build`.
- Keep CI green: backend lint/type/tests and frontend lint/type/build must pass.
- Update `docs/configuration.md` or `docs/setup-checklist.md` when setup changes.
- Prefer fixing root causes over disabling checks or bypassing hooks.
